G29 P3.2 ; interpolate mbl probes
G29 P3.13 ; extrapolate mbl outside probe area
G29 A ; activate mbl

; prepare for purge
M104 S205
G0 X0 Y-4 Z15 F4800 ; move away and ready for the purge
M109 S205

G92 E0
M569 S0 E ; set spreadcycle mode for extruder


; Extrude purge line

